cat("Hello Aliens! It's nice to finally be able to contact you all. Us humans on Earth are glad to be in communication with our fellow occupants of the universe and will like to form a close relationship with you. First off, we would like to tell you that we have around 7.5 billion of us inhabiting our planet and we are continuously trying to find ways to better our everday processes and improve our human race. How many of your kind occupy your planet? Also, attached to this message is a picture of a couple of humans so you can see what we look like. Can you send us a photograph of your kind as well? Us humans on Earth happily look forward to your reply.")